{"tid":1446580,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"事到如今 我地嘅對手已經唔係香港警察咁簡單","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:07:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T15:29:34.000Z","uid":242096,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fa606632d9bf28697235774d3e808b22b209e4c7","tid":1446580,"uid":242096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:07:33.000Z","msg":"大家都知武警混入左警隊<br />\n因爲中央谷住冇得出解放軍<br />\n就換個手段將呢批人滲入香港<br />\n要呢班人擺平呢件事<br />\n佢地比黑警更冇人性更輕視法治<br />\n呢幾日明顯見到對家暴力升級<br />\n騎女途人 射眼 扮示威者 射催淚彈入室內佢地係毫無顧忌 因為背後有中央撐腰<br />\n呢鋪大家如果縮<br />\n香港法治底線將會徹底沉淪<br />\n再冇一國兩際呢回事<br />\n正式成為中國香港 由公安統治<br />\n但如果大家齊上齊落 佢地點都擊退唔到我地 我地就有談判資格 有一絲曙光<br />\n手足我地真係冇得再退 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"7c9549cd8a7903a8bbf7d66edd2190df9259fce4","tid":1446580,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:08:13.000Z","msg":"必及家人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b24adf4ec235bcd458538477d967f34a2ccea07","tid":1446580,"uid":242096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c9549cd8a7903a8bbf7d66edd2190df9259fce4","tid":1446580,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:08:13.000Z","msg":"必及家人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:09:37.000Z","msg":"光復後要佢地一個都走唔甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d4471da859883238a5a734d3b899f8e4e73927","tid":1446580,"uid":65074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:09:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我估林鄭個劇本係<br />\n搵解放軍混入示威者殺一兩隻狗<br />\n靠first blood黎民意翻盤</span>"},{"pid":"fd499